    "minides": "Lexus's flagship body-on-frame SUV, built on the TNGA-F platform, combining Toyota Land Cruiser ruggedness with Lexus luxury and a 304hp twin-turbo diesel V6.",
    "description": "The Lexus LX is the brand's flagship luxury SUV, sharing its ladder-frame TNGA-F platform with the Toyota Land Cruiser. In India it is offered exclusively with a 3.3-litre twin-turbo diesel V6 producing 304 hp and 700 Nm, paired with a 10-speed automatic and full-time four-wheel drive. Two trims are offered: the standard LX 500d Urban and the off-road-focused Overtrail, which adds reinforced underbody protection, a unique Overtrail Monolith dark green cabin theme, and enhanced off-road hardware. The cabin features a triple-display layout, 4-zone climate control, massaging front seats, and Lexus's Level-2 Safety System+ ADAS suite, while retaining genuine off-road tools like Multi-Terrain Select and Crawl Control."
  },
